<section id="rdb_entriez">
    <title>Table: <literal>entries</literal></title>
    <para>Implements the <olink targetptr="core_entry">entry</olink> data type.</para>

    <bridgehead>Columns</bridgehead>
    <itemizedlist>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>lexicographicResourceID int foreign key references
                    lexicographicResource(id)</literal></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>id int</literal>, primary key</para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>headword varchar(255)</literal></para>
        </listitem>
        <listitem>
            <para><literal>homographNumber int</literal></para>
        </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>

    <bridgehead>Comment</bridgehead>
    <para> If the implementation contains only one lexicographic resource, then the column
            <literal>lexicographicResourceID</literal>
        <glossterm>may</glossterm> remain unimplemented. </para>

</section>
